cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual surveillance and re-identification of people using body information. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes an effective matching algorithm using cluster sampling. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) mechanism for accepting new matching solutions. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with matching body information in visual surveillance. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper does not deal with cryptography or security, but it is still possible as the paper deals with surveillance which can have security implications.
